rrow them. And if you=E2=80=99re wrong, and you don=E2=80=99t borrow them, =
then you are naked short, and that=E2=80=99s bad.
Of course here this is silly, it=E2=80=99s a nothing. The SEC mentions nake=
d short selling in the press release, but not in its order; there is no act=
