entional, didn=E2=80=99t save Citadel Securities any money, and doesn=E2=80=
=99t seem to have had any effect on anything but the SEC=E2=80=99s recordke=
eping.
Still.=C2=A0Dumb Money, the GameStop movie, will be in wide release this co=
