" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-d=
ecoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: =
#000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  was laughab=
ly weak</a>.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Elsewhere in the FTC: =E2=80=9C<a href=3D"http=
s://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32838589.290424/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuY=
mxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDktMjYvZnRjLXN1ZXMtYW1hem9uLWlu=
LWxhbmRtYXJrLWFudGl0cnVzdC1jYXNlLW92ZXItbWFya2V0cGxhY2U_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDkyNjI=
zX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3=
Rlcm09MjMwOTI2JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB432=
240f7" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" sty=
le=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width=
: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background=
-color: #ccc;">FTC Sues Amazon</a> in Landmark Antitrust Case Over Marketpl=
ace.=E2=80=9D</p>
