<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">You run an investment firm.</li>=09<l=
i style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">You tell people =E2=80=9Cwe always consider=
