<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/32838589.290424/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9maWxlcy9saXRpZ2F0=
