example, the March 2019 Equity Research Handbook required research notes to=
 include documentation of an issuer=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9CESG &amp; Controvers=
ies.=E2=80=9D Similarly, the July 2020 Credit Research Handbook stated that=
 =E2=80=9Cintegrated initiation report[s] . . . shall consist of . . . ESG =
Analysis.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Whereas in fact it just=C2=A0<em>often=C2=A0</=
