e the paid investment industry magazine article from the Internet.</p></blo=
ckquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I do think that the lowest-hanging possible gr=
eenwashing fruit is =E2=80=9Cif you say you have an ESG checklist, check th=
e checklist every time.=E2=80=9D The checklist doesn=E2=80=99t have to be=
=C2=A0<em>good</em>, it doesn=E2=80=99t have to <em>determine=C2=A0</em>you=
r investing decisions, you just have to=C2=A0<em>check=C2=A0</em>it. But yo=
u do have to check it!</p>
